{"prompt": "Build an intuitive website for a cybersecurity training program. The design should prominently display a dark charcoal.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>CyberSec Training</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #222222; /* Dark charcoal background */\n            color: #eeeeee; /* Light gray text for contrast */\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: #333333; /* Slightly lighter charcoal for header */\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #00cc99 3px solid; /* Accent color */\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            color: #00cc99; /* Accent color */\n        }\n        #main-content {\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        #main-content h2 {\n            color: #00cc99; /* Accent color */\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .course-card {\n            background: #333333;\n            border: 1px solid #00cc99; /* Accent border */\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            transition: transform 0.2s ease-in-out;\n        }\n        .course-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 204, 153, 0.3); /* Subtle accent shadow */\n        }\n        .course-card h3 {\n            color: #00cc99; /* Accent color */\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n        .btn {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background: #00cc99; /* Accent color */\n            color: #222222; /* Dark text for button */\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .btn:hover {\n            background: #00aa80; /* Darker accent on hover */\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            background: #333333; /* Slightly lighter charcoal for footer */\n            color: #aaaaaa;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>CyberSec Training Academy</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <div id=\"main-content\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Unlock Your Potential in Cybersecurity</h2>\n        <p>Our comprehensive training programs are designed to equip you with the skills and knowledge needed to excel in the dynamic field of cybersecurity.</p>\n\n        <div class=\"course-card\">\n            <h3>Foundational Cybersecurity</h3>\n            <p>Learn the core principles of cybersecurity, network security, and threat identification.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn\">Learn More</a>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"course-card\">\n            <h3>Ethical Hacking & Penetration Testing</h3>\n            <p>Master the techniques used by attackers to identify vulnerabilities and secure systems.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn\">Learn More</a>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"course-card\">\n            <h3>Incident Response & Forensics</h3>\n            <p>Develop the skills to manage security breaches and investigate digital incidents.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn\">Learn More</a>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 CyberSec Training Academy. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}